QuestData.Title: Solace for the Highborne
QuestData.Description: I have come to Bashal'Aran to grant peace to the troubled spirits of the Highborne, but I find my hand hesitates with each blow. If you would like to aid me, you would have my gratitude.
QuestData.LogDescription: Kill 6 Cursed Highborne and 6 Writhing Highborne.
QuestData.RewardText: You have my thanks. Though they may not be able to show it, you have the thanks of the Highborne spirits as well.$B$BFare safely, traveler.
